data.description: Natural beauty with a turn-key home in Brooktrails! The home is 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and 1280 sq ft with two decks to enjoy the outdoors and surrounding &  established garden areas and landscaping. Greenhouse to aid in year-round gardening, and two storage buildings. Owned  solar system & dual pane windows to save on energy bills. Central heating and air, but the woodstove is excellent for supplemental heating. With wood accents throughout providing a rustic and natural element,  and vaulted ceilings, this bright and airy home is ready for its new owner(s). Well maintained and  recently painted outside. Chickens are negotiable! A blend of country living with modern amenities.  FHA assumable loan.
